title: Isekai ni Kyuuseishu toshite Yobaremashita ga, Around 30 ni wa Muri nanode, Hissori Book Cafe Hajimemashita.
altTitle: Savior's Bookcafe Story in Another World
I Was Summoned to Another World as a Savior, but Because I'm a Woman in My Thirties That's Impossible, So I Quietly Started a Book Cafe.
The Savior's Book Café Story in Another World
異世界に救世主として喚ばれましたが、アラサーには無理なので、ひっそりブックカフェ始めました。
